Texts.Eng: A sour fruit with a piercing gaze.

Texts.Chs: 这水果是不是一扇通向自己灵魂的窗户？
Texts.Eng: Is this fruit perhaps a window into its own soul?

Texts.Chs: 其次是眼球。叶族人喜欢他们，其他人则失望。
Texts.Eng: Next best thing to eyeballsss. Floran likes them, others are disssturbed.

Texts.Chs: 在宇宙所有的水果中，眼球柠檬可能是最令人毛骨悚然的。
Texts.Eng: Of all the fruit in all the universe, the oculemon may just be the creepiest.

Texts.Chs: 除非精心准备，否则柠檬的某些部分是致命的。
Texts.Eng: Parts of the oculemon are deadly, unless carefully prepared.

Texts.Chs: 果仁应该回头看看你吗？我不知道。。。
Texts.Eng: Should fruit look back at you? I dunno...

Texts.Chs: 鸢尾花是这种奇怪水果最好的部分。
Texts.Eng: The iris is the best part of this strange fruit.

Texts.Chs: 眼球柠檬让我想起了大猩猩。那永远警惕的眼睛。
Texts.Eng: The oculemon reminds me of Big Ape. That ever-watchful eye.
